**Key parallelism:**
- Phase 4 splits: Query Loop Agent does L4, Tools Agent does built-in tools simultaneously
- Red Team runs continuously across all phases
- Phases 1-3 are strictly sequential (each builds on prior)
- Phase 5 depends on Phase 4 (needs tools registered for integration)
- Phase 6 depends on Phase 5 (needs real provider)

