## Agent Communication Protocol

### Team Lead → Agents
- **ASSIGN**: "Implement X. Reference file Y. Target tests Z."
- **REVIEW**: "Tests A, B, C are failing. Diagnose and fix."
- **HOLD**: "Stop work on X, Phase N has a blocking issue."
- **PROCEED**: "Phase N complete. Begin Phase N+1."

### Agents → Team Lead
- **DONE**: "Implemented X. Tests A, B pass. Tests C, D still failing because [reason]."
- **BLOCKED**: "Cannot proceed because [dependency/question]."
- **FINDING**: "Discovered issue with [test/impl/design]. Recommend [fix]."

### Red Team → Team Lead
- **PASS**: "All tests in Phase N pass. `go test -race` clean."
- **FAIL**: "Tests A, B failing. Root cause: [impl bug in file:line] or [test bug in file:line]."
- **REGRESSION**: "Previously passing test X now fails after change Y."
- **NEW_TEST**: "Added N new tests. M pass, K fail."

